==English==

===Adjective===
'''tolerable'''

# Capable of being [[borne]], [[tolerate|tolerated]] or [[endured]]; [[bearable]] or [[endurable]].
# [[Moderate]] in degree; [[mediocre]]; [[passable]], [[acceptable]] or [[so-so]].
# Such as to be [[tolerate|tolerated]] or [[countenance|countenanced]]; [[permissible]]; [[allowable]].
# In [[fair]] health; passably well.

